PrecisAmendment to Schedule A to the FOOD AND DRUGS ACT (Schedule No. 903) removing vaginitis from the disease conditions listed in Schedule A permitting clotrimazole and miconazole, topical antifungal preparations for the treatment of vaginal infections, to be promoted to the general public and permitting the term vaginitis to be used, when appropriate, on the label of drug products.
